<item>
            <title>[LU-6170] Lustre Server 2.1.x support with 2.5.x client</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-6170</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;I have a couple of questions regarding this client / server support.  First, is there a support matrix of which client versions will work this which server versions?  I am specifically interested in Server 2.1.x and the Client 2.5.3.  &lt;br/&gt;
I am running into an issue and I am wondering if it is related the to Client version being so much newer than the server version.  This is the primary error message I am seeing that I believe it causing all of the problems, and I am wondering if it is because of an incompatibility between versions:&lt;br/&gt;
Jan 25 06:11:34 ts-msu-01 kernel: LustreError: 138-a: ls12-MDT0000: A client on nid 10.0.2.154@o2ib&lt;br/&gt;
was evicted due to a lock blocking callback time out: rc -107&lt;/p&gt;</description>
